### 1. Flashcards — Paginated listing (topic 1, 5 per page)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/flashcards?topic_id=1&page=1&limit=5
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Flashcards — Search by keyword
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/flashcards?q=fraction
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Flashcards — Filter by language (Spanish)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/flashcards?lang=es
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Flashcards — Random shuffle (limit 3)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/flashcards?topic_id=1&limit=3&random=true
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. Quizzes — Paginated listing (topic 1)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/quizzes?topic_id=1&page=1&limit=5
Content-Type: application/json

### 6. Quizzes — Filter by difficulty
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/quizzes?topic_id=1&difficulty=med
Content-Type: application/json

### 7. Quizzes — Random order (limit 2)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/quizzes?topic_id=1&limit=2&random=true
Content-Type: application/json

